Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:34.10,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:04.19,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:24.93,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.49,0:27:20.54,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.78,0:29:19.82,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it had to come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?! That sounds like some cheesy movie title!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Legend of Narukami Yu: The Sacred Dragon Sword of Wrath"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he even fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a kung-fu movie, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! {\i1}I'm{\i0} the sponsor here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you're in such high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks for having us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{is this taste good enough?}can you try this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, it feels a bit too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have that special kick to it.{so innovative: punch > kick}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about I add this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Should I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! This is {\i1}your{\i0} going away party, after all!{lit you're the main hero today}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it easy and chat with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are {\i1}you{\i0} taking it easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you've got a knack for this stuff, Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How about putting this outside on the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, never and nope!}Oh, hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, wanna taste it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a taste of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you poison him at his going away party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then{\i1} you{\i0} eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, dude. A farewell party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd actually leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine my days without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, you've got mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot to buy octopus for Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go back to get some!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about we go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'll come back when you have time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think I'll come back during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the May holidays too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray! Then it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna stay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise you'll never forget me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, wanna taste it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a taste of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a knack for this stuff, Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that disgusting thing is what's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then{\i1} you{\i0} eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, you've got mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're surprised to get this letter out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm writing this because there's something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that my game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As you all insisted at the time, I'll abide by the rules of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's still this feeling I can't shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about how it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,About that Midnight Channel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now that I think about it more, before I'd even heard the rumors at the police,}Now I remember... Before I heard the rumors at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{I think someone attacked me when I came to town.}Someone else told me about it when I first came to town...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was intrigued when I noticed that something similar was written on Namatame's report as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't remember who it was that told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Namatame and I both gained our power after coming to Inaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that had something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if any of this will be useful or not, but I hope it can help somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of the Midnight Channel rumor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and their powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You could use Personas from the very start and enter TVs too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you're a person who had power from the beginning, like Namatame and Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something beyond what we can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Midnight Channel and the ability to enter TVs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were really separate, they\N wouldn't fit together like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think the person Adachi mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who told him about the Midnight Channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,also has something to do with the power to enter TVs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I strike gold again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... If they're somehow related...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you have any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we knew when you got your power to enter TVs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we might be able to find the person who started the rumor of the Midnight Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I got this power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I remember having this dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the night I came to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that dream be the reason then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a dream without any discernible catalyst, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The day I arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember going straight to my uncle's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait! I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a taste of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,remember the day I came to town?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We went somewhere before coming home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The gas station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got back from the bathroom,\N you were talking to the weird attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked sick after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're feeling sick, you should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a weird question to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd make it all the way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I never expected this at all.\N You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave the power to Adachi, Namatame, and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the handshake greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A handful of strangers were more than sufficient to stimulate a small place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems the stimulus was stronger than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was enough to envelop this town with fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and later lift it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ameno-Sagiri, ruler of the fog, is merely an aspect of myself that I birthed long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You created the Midnight Channel and spread the rumors of its existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was I who created what you refer to as the Midnight Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is the world humans truly desire?}Has it not given you everything you've wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always your individual wills that would determine what appeared on it.{You yourselves decided what you see there.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans ache to expose their suppressed sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,while the prying eyes around them are curious to see them laid bare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The want to show and the want to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I granted a "window" that catered to both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely gave you what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess this comes with the foolish nature of being mortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{Your foolish desire to only see what you want to see drove the device.}The Midnight Channel only showed you what you wanted to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It showed you your desires in their purest form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see how foolish you've been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want the truth.{YOU CAN'T HANDLE THE TRUTH}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You see only what you want to see and believe only what you want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your desire is for a world enshrouded in fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In eternal, never-lifting fog,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you will always see the world you want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{from kimitachi}That is true happiness for you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How could a world covered in fog bring happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you honestly say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to remember the cruel reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,640)}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the cruel reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to do better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{sensei}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The will of all humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You disturb what they want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They desire to live in the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie! Help! Narukami!{narukami-kun?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop! Please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You only suffer because of your search for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you should just live in a world covered by fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true happiness for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?! That sounds like some cheesy movie title!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Those're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a kung-fu movie, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be together forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm the only one who gets to be {\i1}together{\i0}-together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There she goes again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a taste of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you poison him—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{sensei}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How about putting this outside on the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Try putting these in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that going a bit too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.{not nanako's pudding ;_;}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it had to come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, you'll be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that you'll come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you lose, Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I could break out of my slump thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He can read my moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{sensei}Thank you, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we're apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to be there for you, but it ended up the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of that, we became...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of a tomorrow without everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid I'd lose my friends and have to go on alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had my share of solitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to stay with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't care if it was just a illusion in the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to live a life without being connected to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care as long as I'm with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't need the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As long they're with me, I don't care if it's an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you lose everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,your soul shall never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Never forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a crystal of power which you have nurtured through your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,An orb that repels fabrications of all sorts, dispels lies, and shines upon the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your true form?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It matters not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The will of all mankind will pull you under again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the will of so few surpass the will of all mankind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for humans to grasp the truth with their own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the one who gets to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends are no longer with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go on living alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:22:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,am not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of endless struggle, wouldn't it be easier to wrap oneself in lies and live in blissful ignorance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.21,0:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,human potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think yourself a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If only they'd open their eyes and look ahead, they could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dispel the fog that covers our path!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in the Myriad Truths{幾万の真言} ahead of us!{what was this in the game again? myriad truths or something?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Myriad Truths?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.24,0:24:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.86,0:24:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have lifted the fog in this world, as well as the fog in your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.41,0:24:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And whether that will lead to happiness or not rests upon your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.42,0:24:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.96,0:24:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Children of man...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.88,0:24:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.31,0:24:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.60,0:25:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I still inside the TV world?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.56,0:25:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be what the TV world is supposed to look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.69,0:25:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wonderful! A wonderful turn of your life.}How marvelous! A turning point in your destiny, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.24,0:25:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This journey was a fruitful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.99,0:25:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the fog of lies has lifted,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.25,0:25:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing to prevent you from moving forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.04,0:25:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You are free to walk your own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.21,0:25:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the last time we summon you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.09,0:25:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.60,0:25:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.89,0:25:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.35,0:25:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.98,0:25:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.11,0:25:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to see this sight again for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.11,0:25:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere in this world used to look like this a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.49,0:25:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch where you're rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.95,0:25:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{senpai}You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.87,0:25:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.24,0:25:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.37,0:26:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{senpai}Dude!{the fuck?}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.09,0:26:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Our contract has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.01,0:26:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My own duties end here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.18,0:26:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a truly remarkable guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.56,0:26:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go forth and see with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.82,0:26:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,976)}See the world you have won... \N{brainchild was here} And the bright, magnificent future...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.67,0:26:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,{added this line for the sake of timing, feel free to change/remove}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.71,0:26:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.09,0:26:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck over there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.18,0:26:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens on your end, we'll come running!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.30,0:27:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we meet again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.06,0:27:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you!{gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.23,0:27:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye and take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be looking forward to seeing you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.61,0:27:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.90,0:27:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.24,0:27:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Buh-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.78,0:27:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.20,0:27:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care too!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.66,0:27:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.12,0:27:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay well until we meet again someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.79,0:27:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll always be my "Master"!{"You'll always be my bear-y best friend!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.80,0:27:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't forget about us over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.38,0:27:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.51,0:27:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.39,0:27:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best! You'd better not run away too!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.31,0:27:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always remember our time together!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.06,0:27:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance doesn't matter to us! Even if we're separated, we're still friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.23,0:27:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never, ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.20,0:27:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,forget you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.11,0:29:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.12,0:29:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad he won't be around, but we'll be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.83,0:29:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter how far apart we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.46,0:29:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Our hearts are connected, that won't change!}{persona references in KC and KC references in persona. makes sense}The bonds we made will remain strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.71,0:29:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're connected with the people you trust.}Everyone's heart{kokoro} is connected to the people they know and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.34,0:29:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's those bonds that let us all search for our purpose in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.18,0:29:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it's a purpose you believe in,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.85,0:29:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,there'll always be someone who can help you fulfill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.31,0:29:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, me, and everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.23,0:29:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no barriers. Our hearts are one.{THE WORLD INSIDE PEOPLE'S HEARTS OMG}
